// privshape's behavior. `Hidden` is defined here in the `#module` band ‚Äî a shape MAY live in #module
// (it is private to its device), but then no public shape backs the datasheet's `Hidden[4]`
// requirement. Support file for datasheet_req_private_shape.arche.
// RUN: true
#module

Hidden :: arche { z }

tick :: map (query { z }) {
  z = z + 1.0;
}
